gomodel:SYNGO_1739  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig. 2B, shows the enrichment of FYN in the PSD fraction\n\nLiteral:\n\"(B) Adult rat brain was fractionated to isolate the SPM and PSD. Samples from each fraction (10 μg of protein per lane) were immunoblotted with STEP61, PSD-95, Fyn, β-actin, and synaptophysin antibodies.\". Experimental description: Rat brains were used for the biochemical fractionation\n\nLiteral form M&M:\n\"Subcellular Fractionation of Rodent Brain Tissues and Cultured Neurons. The\nfractionation experiment was performed following standard methods (53). Brain tissues dissected out from adult female rats,...\"" ;
